@vrv I have the same issue on MacOS X when running the java example

```
$ javac -cp libtensorflow-1.0.0-PREVIEW1.jar LabelImage.java
$ java -cp libtensorflow-1.0.0-PREVIEW1.jar:. -Djava.library.path=./jni LabelImage
$ java -cp libtensorflow-1.0.0-PREVIEW1.jar:. -Djava.library.path=./jni LabelImage ./ ./example-400x288.jpg 
Failed to read [./tensorflow_inception_graph.pb]: ./tensorflow_inception_graph.pb
```

I have the native dylib library and the inceptionv5 model in the path:
